============================================================
🚀 AWS Cloud Governance Dashboard - Backend
============================================================

📍 Server: http://localhost:3001
📋 Health: http://localhost:3001/health
💬 Chat WebSocket: ws://localhost:3001/api/chat

📚 Available Endpoints:
  GET  /api/accounts              - List all AWS accounts
  GET  /api/session/status        - Check session status
  POST /api/session/refresh       - Refresh AWS session
  POST /api/scan                  - Start resource scan
  GET  /api/scan/:jobId/stream    - SSE stream for scan progress
  GET  /api/resources             - Query discovered resources
  GET  /api/resources/stats       - Get resource statistics

🔒 Security Endpoints:
  POST /api/security/audit        - Start security audit
  GET  /api/security/findings     - Get security findings
  GET  /api/security/compliance   - Get compliance report
  GET  /api/security/alerts       - Get security alerts
  GET  /api/security/alerts/stream - SSE stream for real-time alerts

💰 Cost Endpoints:
  POST /api/cost/report           - Generate cost report
  GET  /api/cost/summary          - Get cost summary
  GET  /api/cost/trends           - Get cost trends
  GET  /api/cost/forecast         - Get cost forecast
  GET  /api/cost/dashboard        - Get cost dashboard summary
  POST /api/cost/refresh          - Refresh cost data
  GET  /api/cost/budgets          - Get all budgets
  POST /api/cost/budgets          - Create new budget

💬 Chat Endpoints:
  WS   /api/chat                  - WebSocket for AI chat
  POST /api/chat/message          - Send chat message
  GET  /api/chat/suggestions      - Get suggested questions
  DELETE /api/chat/session/:id    - Clear chat session

🏢 Organization Endpoints:
  GET  /api/organization          - Get organization structure
  GET  /api/organization/accounts - List all accounts
  GET  /api/organization/groups   - List account groups
  GET  /api/organization/insights - Get organization insights
  GET  /api/organization/hierarchy - Get account hierarchy
  POST /api/organization/groups   - Create account group

📊 Analytics Endpoints:
  GET  /api/analytics/aggregated  - Get aggregated metrics
  POST /api/analytics/comparison  - Compare accounts
  GET  /api/analytics/benchmarks/:id - Benchmark account
  GET  /api/analytics/trends      - Get organization trends
  POST /api/analytics/chargeback  - Generate chargeback report
  POST /api/analytics/search      - Federated search
  GET  /api/analytics/summary     - Get executive summary

✅ Features: Cost per Resource + AI Chat Panel
